## 5.02-login-with-metamask

1. Open 5.02-login-with-metamask in VSCode
$ nvm use v16.13.1
$ node -v
v16.13.1

2. Make sure you have Metamask install as a plugin in your browser

3. Add BSCTest Network using the information belows
Name: BSC Testnet
RPC Endpoints: (choose one)
https://data-seed-prebsc-1-s1.binance.org:8545/
https://data-seed-prebsc-2-s1.binance.org:8545/
https://data-seed-prebsc-1-s2.binance.org:8545/
ChainId: 97
Native Token: BNB
Block Explorer: https://testnet.bscscan.com/

4. Run yarn to install dependency
$ yarn

5. Run truffle compile
$ truffle complie

6. Run typechain to gen typescript version of contract
$ yarn run typechain --target=web3-v1 'build/contracts/*.json'

7. Run yarn dev
$ yarn dev

8. Play around the UI

9. Explain sourcecode in pages/index.vue